These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, may
2 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig
1. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Birthday           | may | november |
| Pet   | guinea-pig     | lizard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, yellow
1. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing   | cooking      |
| Color   | white | yellow |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
